     7 SECURITY. APENAS O AUTOR PODE MODIFICA-LO.
     8
     9 ENVIRONMENT     DIVISION.
    10 CONFIGURATION SECTION.
    11 SOURCE-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    12 OBJECT-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    13 SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    14
    15 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
    16 FILE-CONTROL.
    17     SELECT   CADALU      ASSIGN      TO       DISK
    18     ORGANIZATION  IS         LINE        SEQUENTIAL.
    19     SELECT   CADATU        ASSIGN     TO       DISK
    20     ORGANIZATION  IS         LINE        SEQUENTIAL.
    21
    22 DATA           DIVISION.
    23 FILE SECTION.
    24
    25 FD  CADALU
    26     LABEL   RECORD  STANDARD
    27     VALUE    OF FILE-ID    IS          "CADALU.DAT".
    28 01  REG-ENT.
    29     02 NUM-ENT           PIC 9(05).
    30     02 NOME-ENT          PIC X(20).
    31     02 NOTA1-ENT         PIC 9(02)V99.
    32     02 NOTA2-ENT         PIC 9(02)V99.
    33     02 NOTA3-ENT         PIC 9(02)V99.
    34
    35 FD  CADATU
    36     LABEL   RECORD  STANDARD
    37     VALUE   OF FILE-ID    IS   "CADATU.DAT".
    38 01  REG-SAI.
    39     02 NUM-SAI           PIC 9(05).
    40     02 MEDIA-SAI         PIC 9(02)V99.
    41
    42 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    43     77 FIM-ARQ          PIC X(03)    VALUE "NAO".
    44     77 MEDIA-CONT       PIC 9(02)V99.
    45
    46 PROCEDURE        DIVISION.
    47
    48 EXEMPLO.
    49     PERFORM INICIO.
    50     PERFORM PRINCIPAL
    51       UNTIL FIM-ARQ EQUAL "SIM".
    52     PERFORM TERMINO
    53     STOP RUN.
    54 INICIO.
    55     OPEN INPUT CADALU
    56          OUTPUT CADATU.
    57     PERFORM LEITURA.
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 18-Mar-25 17:37 Page   2
*                                      EXERC3.CBL
    58
    59     LEITURA.
    60         READ CADALU
    61            AT END
    62            MOVE "SIM" TO FIM-ARQ.
    63 PRINCIPAL.
    64     PERFORM GRAVACAO.
    65     PERFORM LEITURA.
    66
    67     GRAVACAO.
    68         COMPUTE MEDIA-CONT=(NOTA1-ENT + NOTA2-ENT + NOTA3-ENT)/3.
    69         MOVE NUM-ENT TO NUM-SAI.
    70         MOVE MEDIA-CONT TO MEDIA-SAI.
    71         WRITE REG-SAI.
    72
    73 TERMINO.
    74     CLOSE CADALU
    75           CADATU.
